overview: A host of landscapes leads us on an unparalleled journey, from imagined realms of plenitude to the beauty and magic glimpsed in the everyday. The film is comprised of high-definition nighttime video images of a very busy oceanfront beach in Shenzhen, the high waves and circulating crowds of swimmers echoed in the rhythmic shifts of speed used in editing.
title: Seascape #1 Night, China Shenzhen 05
